<Base
  title="Gmail vs Outlook Sending Limits for Cold Email: Official Caps vs Safe Volumes"
  description="Google Workspace allows 2,000 messages/day; Exchange Online caps external recipients at 2,000/day. But official limits aren't safe cold email volumes — those are 50–100/day per mailbox."
